dct_title_s: Subject nationalities of the German alliance : from the Allies' peace terms as stated in their reply to President Wilson's note of 19th Dec. 1916 : [Eurasia]
dct_description_sm: This map drawn from German sources (especially the All-Deutscher Atlas edited by Paul Langhans and published at Gotha by Justus Perthes in 1905) shows the nationalities which are actually subject to Germany and her Allies.; Includes text, statistics of "Total populations of the German alliance, censuses of 1910," and tables showing populations by nationality.
